{"tid":431420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅磡女子虛報遭南亞漢毆劫　警列傻人發現","createTime":"2017-10-10T16:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T01:20:43.000Z","uid":122,"like":134,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c649847c29a4a4e97aa5242db13a36932dfe86","tid":431420,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"10月10日(二) 22:02更新     12:15建立<br />\n<strong>紅磡女子虛報遭南亞漢毆劫　警列傻人發現</strong><br />\n<br />\n紅磡有女子虛報遭南亞漢毆劫，上午11時許，姓柯（42歲）女子報稱行經港鐵紅磡車站對開時，突遭一名南亞漢從後揮拳襲擊，對方趁亂搶去其2000港元現金及八達通後逃去。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報迅速到場，發現柯女頭部受傷，將她送院治理。不過，警方翻查「天眼」及經過深入調查後，發現有人虛報遇劫，案件改列傻人發現處理。"},{"pid":"77dc6e49e33dcd40324c9136a3c2675720c1504e","tid":431420,"uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:15:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a58031813e5b10f07604d532b52bf35dc791aa8","tid":431420,"uid":389,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:15:42.000Z","msg":"同林子建差唔多"},{"pid":"a6cfd6594de70f07d58a9e5c3979024383f1e280","tid":431420,"uid":36964,"like":5,"dislike":12,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:16:55.000Z","msg":"咩係傻人發現?"},{"pid":"ad02c316d1de471dc5e46bd7afcb889a7ab17fb8","tid":431420,"uid":61832,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:18:14.000Z","msg":"唔係浪費警力？<br />\n除非條女有精神問題"},{"pid":"b07f654fa1ec64c10ca0ca13ecde6a3ced8472ad","tid":431420,"uid":389,"like":77,"dislike":0,"score":77,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:19:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩係傻人發現?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/11/001911_1937313c706aea19b613debc1dd4bcab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F11%2F001911_1937313c706aea19b613debc1dd4bcab.jpg&h=07dac556&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"561e3b1c8a9052766032b9f1831edfd31388590f","tid":431420,"uid":82262,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0